01:57:29,625 --> 01:57:31,291
Hey.

1407
01:57:31,750 --> 01:57:33,000
Hey.

1408
01:57:35,333 --> 01:57:37,166
This is Sairoong,

1409
01:57:39,333 --> 01:57:42,916
her young colleague
