-Besides being young,
-Hello.

1428
01:58:42,916 --> 01:58:45,125
he's good looking too.

1429
01:58:56,166 --> 01:58:57,416
Since when?

1430
01:58:57,666 --> 01:58:58,791
What?

1431
01:58:59,000 --> 01:59:01,291
When did you decide
to start seeing that boy?

1432
