I never forgot my late husband.

1437
01:59:33,791 --> 01:59:36,333
It's true
that there is a new man in my life.

1438
01:59:40,708 --> 01:59:42,291
She told Sairoong about him

1439
01:59:42,375 --> 01:59:44,583
and the stories he told her

1440
01:59:44,666 --> 01:59:46,458
about the running schedule,

1441
01:59:46,791 --> 01:59:48,291
Milo's principle,

1442
01:59:48,666 --> 01:59:51,541
and the devil at the 35-km mark.

1443
01:59:54,000 --> 01:59:56,791
Before Lumpini park was closed that night,

1444
01:59:57,416 --> 01:59:59,166
Sairoong asked her...

1445
01:59:59,250 --> 02:00:00,375
Hey.

1446
02:00:01,166 --> 02:00:03,083
Are you sure you're not going crazy?

1447
02:00:05,666 --> 02:00:07,833
I understand you must be lonely, but...

1448
02:00:08,666 --> 02:00:09,958
I am lonely

1449
02:00:11,500 --> 02:00:13,166
but I don't want to be sad.

1450
02:00:15,750 --> 02:00:17,375
She wasn't sure

1451
02:00:17,458 --> 02:00:20,250
if Sairoong would accept her or not

1452
02:00:20,750 --> 02:00:23,500
if she told her the real reason

1453
02:00:23,583 --> 02:00:25,000
in her mind.

1454
02:00:25,166 --> 02:00:26,958
I can't accept this.

1455
02:01:08,791 --> 02:01:09,916
That night,

1456
02:01:10,583 --> 02:01:12,583
she laid on the sofa

1457
02:01:14,416 --> 02:01:16,916
and stared at the faint light

1458
02:01:17,416 --> 02:01:20,833
shining through the curtains
like in those Kazakhstan films

1459
02:01:21,291 --> 02:01:23,458
with a heavy heart.

1460
02:02:17,291 --> 02:02:19,208
Hello, this is Pongsakorn speaking.

1461
02:02:19,291 --> 02:02:23,208
Please leave a message
after the beeping sound.

1462
02:02:24,666 --> 02:02:25,833
Thank you.

1463
