See? I told you it would only take a day.

1465
02:02:47,541 --> 02:02:49,333
You always exaggerate things.

1466
02:02:50,333 --> 02:02:54,208
-I told you so and you didn't believe me.
-The beach here is beautiful.

1467
02:02:54,291 --> 02:02:57,416
Why don't you show me
how to dive in the pool here?

1468
02:02:57,791 --> 02:03:00,916
I've shown you many times.
You must be bored of it by now.

1469
02:03:01,333 --> 02:03:05,083
This week is really busy.
