Be reasonable, Pat.

1488
02:07:59,333 --> 02:08:00,458
She spoke to him

1489
02:08:00,541 --> 02:08:03,791
trying to keep it down

1490
02:08:03,958 --> 02:08:06,208
so that it would not echo.

1491
02:08:06,375 --> 02:08:07,875
But at that moment,

1492
02:08:07,958 --> 02:08:09,958
she couldn't 

1493
02:08:10,083 --> 02:08:12,166
keep her voice calm.

1494
02:08:12,291 --> 02:08:13,708
If I want to keep seeing you,

1495
02:08:14,333 --> 02:08:15,666
I will go running with you.

1496
02:08:16,958 --> 02:08:18,458
But honestly,

1497
02:08:19,041 --> 02:08:20,583
this has gone too far.

1498
02:08:21,875 --> 02:08:23,750
You shouldn't waste your time on me.

1499
02:08:25,541 --> 02:08:28,041
Do you know
that you're the most pitiful one?

1500
02:08:32,541 --> 02:08:33,583
Why?

1501
02:08:34,083 --> 02:08:34,958
Hey.

1502
02:08:35,791 --> 02:08:37,208
You know Milo's principle.

1503
02:08:37,625 --> 02:08:39,791
You planned a 40km running schedule.

1504
02:08:40,708 --> 02:08:42,583
How come you don't know
the answer to this?

1505
02:08:44,333 --> 02:08:45,875
These last couple of months,

1506
02:08:46,666 --> 02:08:48,833
I've been trying to tell you

1507
02:08:48,916 --> 02:08:50,375
that I like you.

1508
02:09:09,291 --> 02:09:10,958
Your family won't be okay with me.

1509
02:09:15,333 --> 02:09:17,333
No family would be okay with me.

1510
02:09:20,833 --> 02:09:22,875
My family isn't okay
with the marathon either.

1511
02:09:24,833 --> 02:09:26,166
In 20 years,

1512
02:09:26,458 --> 02:09:28,958
do you want to feed me the food
that old people eat before going to bed?

1513
02:09:29,916 --> 02:09:31,333
If you want to have dinner,

1514
02:09:31,416 --> 02:09:33,833
go eat with your mom at home.

1515
02:09:36,250 --> 02:09:38,791
You don't want to regret it later, right?

1516
02:09:41,666 --> 02:09:42,791
Do you regret

1517
02:09:45,041 --> 02:09:46,875
anything now?

1518
02:09:55,583 --> 02:09:58,458
The devil at the 35-km and 36-km mark,

1519
02:09:59,166 --> 02:10:01,833
did it not warn you
about your actions now?

