1525
02:10:32,583 --> 02:10:34,791
I wanted you to think
I didn't know anything about you.

1526
02:10:43,500 --> 02:10:44,750
What if

1527
02:10:47,458 --> 02:10:49,166
I was a normal guy

1528
02:10:50,208 --> 02:10:51,500
and you were

1529
02:10:51,583 --> 02:10:53,166
a normal girl,

1530
02:10:53,791 --> 02:10:55,208
without your husband...

1531
02:10:57,500 --> 02:10:59,083
could we be together?

1532
02:11:08,583 --> 02:11:10,041
What makes you think we could?

1533
02:11:12,208 --> 02:11:13,583
My instinct tells me so.

1534
02:11:20,166 --> 02:11:22,458
Either you watch too many movies,
or you are too young.

1535
02:11:25,166 --> 02:11:26,416
I am young,

1536
02:11:27,208 --> 02:11:28,666
but not that young.

1537
02:11:30,833 --> 02:11:32,166
I'm sorry.

1538
02:11:33,000 --> 02:11:34,916
I am not amused by your teenage quip.

1539
02:11:47,208 --> 02:11:48,291
Right before

1540
02:11:49,125 --> 02:11:51,000
you came to see me,

1541
02:11:52,500 --> 02:11:54,458
I was looking at myself in the mirror.

1542
02:11:57,125 --> 02:11:59,500
It was the first time in a few months

1543
02:12:00,958 --> 02:12:02,958
that I took a good look at myself.

1544
02:12:04,791 --> 02:12:06,458
I never felt

1545
02:12:07,250 --> 02:12:08,916
like I betrayed my husband

1546
02:12:09,916 --> 02:12:11,125
until today.

1547
02:12:19,041 --> 02:12:20,083
Do you know

1548
02:12:22,083 --> 02:12:24,458
what promise I have given him
at his grave?

1549
02:12:33,916 --> 02:12:36,208
I promised
that I would not love another man.

1550
02:12:43,458 --> 02:12:45,041
Thank you for introducing me to marathons.

1551
02:12:51,875 --> 02:12:53,750
But I don't want to see your face anymore.

1552
