and the bullet
killed an unlucky crocodile...

1555
02:13:42,666 --> 02:13:44,000
After that day,

1556
02:13:44,791 --> 02:13:47,416
she thought about starting her life over.

1557
02:13:49,458 --> 02:13:52,250
But she could only turn on the TV

1558
02:13:53,416 --> 02:13:56,958
and pretend to watch Sairoong's show.

1559
02:13:58,250 --> 02:13:59,416
Or sometimes

1560
02:13:59,500 --> 02:14:01,291
she would turn her back towards the park

1561
02:14:01,750 --> 02:14:05,791
while the Skytrain approached
the park's station.

1562
02:14:12,458 --> 02:14:14,416
On a sunny day,

1563
02:14:14,500 --> 02:14:16,833
she thought of retiring her shoes,

1564
02:14:17,125 --> 02:14:20,041
just like those
retired football players do

1565
02:14:20,166 --> 02:14:22,333
when they stop using their studs.

1566
02:14:33,125 --> 02:14:35,916
It was a Saturday morning in October.

1567
02:14:36,166 --> 02:14:37,750
Her mom came to visit

1568
02:14:38,083 --> 02:14:40,666
with souvenirs from China.

1569
02:14:41,666 --> 02:14:43,666
Her mom asked her about work.

1570
02:14:43,750 --> 02:14:45,375
When are you going back to work?

1571
02:14:48,208 --> 02:14:49,333
In a while.

1572
02:14:49,416 --> 02:14:52,291
And then her mom made breakfast for her.

1573
02:14:56,291 --> 02:14:58,166
Even though her mom
didn't make it obvious,

1574
02:14:59,208 --> 02:15:02,833
a lot of little things made her feel

1575
02:15:03,416 --> 02:15:06,125
like her mom wanted to talk
about something.

1576
02:15:21,791 --> 02:15:22,750
Mom.

1577
02:15:25,833 --> 02:15:27,083
Did Sairoong tell you?

1578
02:15:27,625 --> 02:15:29,416
Yes, yesterday.

1579
02:15:30,291 --> 02:15:32,166
I met her and she told me.

1580
02:15:36,541 --> 02:15:37,708
Oh, no.

1581
02:15:37,875 --> 02:15:40,875
She couldn't think of anything
to say to her mom.

1582
02:15:40,958 --> 02:15:42,666
She told me
you're going to run a marathon.

1583
02:15:43,250 --> 02:15:45,208
Be careful not to break your legs.

1584
