On my way up,
someone asked me to give this to you.

1585
02:15:50,958 --> 02:15:53,708
I guess he tried to call
but your phone must be off.

1586
02:15:58,291 --> 02:15:59,958
YOU'RE INVITED TO BANGKOK GIANT MARATHON

1587
02:16:11,708 --> 02:16:15,000
