1588
02:16:15,291 --> 02:16:16,500
This time,

1589
02:16:16,958 --> 02:16:19,416
he really made her heart skip a beat.

1590
02:16:26,208 --> 02:16:27,541
Taste it.

1591
02:16:29,833 --> 02:16:31,500
-It's good.
-Okay.

1592
02:16:31,583 --> 02:16:34,416
And who was that guy?
Kids these days are so good looking.

1593
02:16:35,416 --> 02:16:36,833
Was he your trainer?

1594
02:16:37,541 --> 02:16:39,541
That's good. He can look after you.

1595
02:16:46,333 --> 02:16:49,041
While her mom was cooking that morning,

1596
02:16:49,583 --> 02:16:53,375
food was the last thing on her mind.

1597
02:16:59,083 --> 02:17:00,875
These past few months,

1598
02:17:00,958 --> 02:17:03,916
practicing for the marathon
gave her peace.

1599
02:17:04,458 --> 02:17:08,041
Living life seemed to get easier.

1600
02:17:29,791 --> 02:17:32,500
But right now she is afraid that

1601
02:17:32,583 --> 02:17:34,708
if she stays in this room,

1602
02:17:34,791 --> 02:17:37,375
she will keep staring into the mirror

1603
02:17:37,500 --> 02:17:40,000
over and over again.

1604
02:17:52,333 --> 02:17:53,333
Ten.

1605
02:17:53,958 --> 02:17:55,083
Nine.

1606
02:17:55,541 --> 02:17:56,833
Eight.

1607
02:17:57,541 --> 02:17:58,750
Seven.

1608
02:17:58,958 --> 02:18:00,208
Six.

1609
02:18:00,833 --> 02:18:02,041
Five.

1610
02:18:02,333 --> 02:18:03,416
Four.

1611
02:18:03,916 --> 02:18:05,125
Three.

1612
02:18:05,208 --> 02:18:06,333
Two.

1613
02:18:06,416 --> 02:18:07,791
One.

1614
02:18:20,041 --> 02:18:21,666
I want my new life to begin

