02:20:17,750 --> 02:20:19,916
the point of the race

1633
02:20:20,416 --> 02:20:22,083
where we all feel alone

1634
02:20:22,291 --> 02:20:24,375
and must make a decision.

1635
02:20:25,083 --> 02:20:27,000
We must ask ourselves

1636
02:20:27,083 --> 02:20:28,958
"How badly do we want to finish?"

1637
02:20:29,041 --> 02:20:30,375
Miss.

1638
02:20:31,666 --> 02:20:32,791
Do you need a ride?

1639
02:20:33,041 --> 02:20:35,666
And we must find the answer on our own.

1640
02:20:35,750 --> 02:20:36,916
What kilometer is this?

1641
02:20:37,208 --> 02:20:38,583
I don't know.

1642
02:20:39,666 --> 02:20:42,208
She never thought

1643
02:20:42,958 --> 02:20:45,666
she would end up on this road

1644
02:20:46,083 --> 02:20:48,416
at the age of 42.

1645
02:20:55,083 --> 02:20:56,333
Thank you.

1646
02:20:56,916 --> 02:20:59,041
Miss, just a bit further.

1647
02:21:04,666 --> 02:21:06,666
You haven't stopped running
in the opposite direction.

1648
02:21:06,958 --> 02:21:08,500
What took you so long?

1649
02:21:08,833 --> 02:21:10,708
I was waiting for you at the finish line.

1650
02:21:35,750 --> 02:21:37,458
Yesterday, did you tell my mom

1651
02:21:37,541 --> 02:21:38,833
that you would look after me?

1652
02:21:47,666 --> 02:21:48,875
Well...

1653
02:21:50,333 --> 02:21:52,333
It wasn't exactly like that.

1654
02:21:55,041 --> 02:21:56,666
What did my mom tell you?

1655
02:22:01,083 --> 02:22:02,166
Well.

1656
02:22:04,083 --> 02:22:05,958
-She said--
-I'm kidding.

1657
02:22:07,166 --> 02:22:08,291
Let's go!

1658
02:22:08,458 --> 02:22:11,666
She was thinking that in reality,

1659
02:22:11,875 --> 02:22:14,708
her past and memories did not exist.

1660
02:22:16,166 --> 02:22:17,791
Right now,

1661
02:22:17,875 --> 02:22:20,500
it was just a matter

1662
02:22:20,583 --> 02:22:22,041
of moving her legs

1663
02:22:22,125 --> 02:22:23,666
to keep moving forward.

1664
02:22:37,625 --> 02:22:38,708
You go first.

1665
02:22:39,208 --> 02:22:40,458
Come with me.

1666
02:22:40,791 --> 02:22:42,541
Come on. Just a bit more.

1667
