You go first.

1668
02:22:44,041 --> 02:22:45,166
I can't go on anymore.

1669
02:22:50,416 --> 02:22:52,583
Stop being pessimistic.

1670
02:22:52,958 --> 02:22:55,791
How hard can 2km be?

1671
02:22:57,125 --> 02:22:58,625
Tomorrow is a new day.

1672
